Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.15,0:00:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A Hero. A bringer of peace\Nwho battles monsters and protects people.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.70,0:00:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The young boy, Dai,\Nwas raised by monsters.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.58,0:00:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He decided to fight the Dark Army\Nafter being trained by the Hero, Avan.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.92,0:00:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Traveling with Popp, the Mage, they were\Nlater joined by Maam, a Warrior Priest.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.39,0:00:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Monsters of the Dark Lord Hadlar's Six\NLegions attacked these Disciples of Avan.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.81,0:00:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They defeated Crocodine\Nof the Furfang Legion,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.48,0:00:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and were victorious against\NHyunckel of the Undead Legion.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.49,0:00:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dai continues on the path of a Hero.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.78,0:01:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}His next adversary is\NBlizzblaze General Flazzard.{\i0}
