Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.89,0:01:29.23,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}are itsukarada?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.40,0:01:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Being honest became whining{\i0}
