Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.32,0:01:34.69,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}nigenai koto ga tsuyosa ni natta{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.86,0:01:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Have you found it yet?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.86,0:01:37.99,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}naa mitsukaranai?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.16,0:01:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not confidence, your true self{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.16,0:01:42.37,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}jishin janaku jibun jishin{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.66,0:01:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There must be something\NI've forgotten that I still haven't found{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.66,0:01:47.87,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kitto mada sagasetenai wasuremono ga aruhazu{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.04,0:01:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Words I want to say\NThat I still haven't said{\i0}
