Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.25,0:02:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,BLIZZBLAZE GENERAL FLAZZARD
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.36,0:03:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Maam? You seem blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.37,0:03:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.12,0:03:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.46,0:03:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,About Hyunckel?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.00,0:03:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.55,0:03:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you, well, like...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.72,0:03:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you like him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.34,0:03:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.14,0:03:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.93,0:03:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But, when I looked into his sad eyes,\NI wanted to help him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.48,0:03:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to be by his side.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.73,0:03:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I just got that feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.65,0:03:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry! It's okay. He's not dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.86,0:03:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,After all Dai and I threw at him,\Nhe was fit as a fiddle, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.54,0:03:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.62,0:03:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He was even Undead Legion Commander.\NHe wouldn't die so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.04,0:03:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right. Thank you, Popp.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.09,0:03:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.92,0:04:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He must be alive.\NHe was a Disciple of Avan, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.68,0:04:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh man! What the hell am I doing?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.30,0:04:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Here I am, talking up my rival\Nfor some reason!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.43,0:04:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.85,0:04:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.48,0:04:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, it's like new! Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.03,0:04:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,They used to call me\Nthe Papnica Inventor King!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.57,0:04:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to being\N"the greatest swordsman in Papnica"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.99,0:04:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we're all set! Let's go rescue Leona!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.04,0:04:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The problem is just where is the Princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.17,0:04:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He's right. She's missing, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.80,0:04:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Where to look\Nin this vast continent of Holkia?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.47,0:04:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess we'll have to take it slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.97,0:04:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But if we don't hurry, the next Legion\NCommander of the Dark Army might show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.27,0:04:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Leona...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.73,0:04:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.10,0:04:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What's it, old timer?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.90,0:05:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The temple! We should go to the temple!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.32,0:05:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The temple?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.82,0:05:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, old timer,\Nwhat's in this ruined temple?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.99,0:05:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The temple has a basement warehouse.\NTry to find the entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.25,0:05:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This won't be easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.54,0:05:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What's in that warehouse?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.30,0:05:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Signal flares!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.80,0:05:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Signal flares?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.88,0:05:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Papnica has flares that use\Ngunpowder to send signals during battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.68,0:05:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh. With gunpowder?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.27,0:05:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,If we find and launch one, the Princess\Nis sure to see it wherever she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.23,0:05:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.48,0:05:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If we launch\Na red signal flare of victory,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.65,0:05:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure the Her Majesty will feel\Nit's safe enough to show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.95,0:05:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.29,0:05:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh! This might actually be it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.54,0:05:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no good!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.75,0:06:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.29,0:06:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But... I don't think we can move all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.55,0:06:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me! Everybody get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.31,0:06:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,He seems excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.98,0:06:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,He probably can't wait\Nto test his strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.31,0:06:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I told him he beat Hyunckel\Nwithout the power of his mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.69,0:06:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's test out whether I can\Nuse that skill or not!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.03,0:06:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Mera!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.45,0:06:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You moron! Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.92,0:06:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Fire Earth Slash!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.64,0:06:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! I really did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.06,0:06:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You moron! Of all the attacks to use!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.93,0:07:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,There's gunpowder down there! Gunpowder!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.19,0:07:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.73,0:07:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,They've ignited! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.85,0:07:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,A total loss.\NAll the signal flares were blown away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.10,0:07:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey dummy, why couldn't you use Hyado\Nfor an Ice Earth Slash or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.02,0:07:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.86,0:07:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.90,0:07:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, at least the flares were launched.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.03,0:07:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think Princess Leona\Ngot the message?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.57,0:08:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I dunno. With that crazy display, she\Nmight get suspicious and stay hidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.75,0:08:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.67,0:08:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.51,0:08:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.71,0:08:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.55,0:08:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a bird.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.55,0:08:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it a monster?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.51,0:08:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.60,0:08:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.02,0:08:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The Papnica Balloon Ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.10,0:08:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Balloon Ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.31,0:08:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a vehicle that travels by air!\NThe royal family uses it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.03,0:08:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.57,0:08:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Take us down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.87,0:08:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Baduck!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.54,0:08:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.20,0:08:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.58,0:08:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.67,0:08:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.58,0:08:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.13,0:08:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.43,0:09:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Amy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.89,0:09:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Baduck, did you send up those flares?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.44,0:09:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You know her, old timer?\NIntroduce me, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.98,0:09:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Fool! Show some respect!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.40,0:09:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Lady Amy,\None of the Papnica Troika!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.99,0:09:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,A woman that young? I was thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.29,0:09:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We're the Papnica Troika!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.67,0:09:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Those strange flares went up,\Nso we came to check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.09,0:09:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I left the Princess with Apollo and Marin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.05,0:09:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,By Princess, you mean Leona, right?!\NIs she okay?! Where is she?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.39,0:09:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.68,0:09:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a friend of Leona's! My name is Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.31,0:09:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai? You're Dai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.35,0:09:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. This young man is\Nthe Hero Her Majesty always talks about.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.07,0:09:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,This young man and his friends\Nhave already vanquished the Undead Legion.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.53,0:10:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You can all rest easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.66,0:10:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.70,0:10:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Vanquished the Undead Legion?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.83,0:10:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really Dai, the Hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.13,0:10:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a weapon\Nof the Papnica royal family!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.09,0:10:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Leona gave it to me. It's my treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.81,0:10:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand. Come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.14,0:10:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The Princess waits at Valge Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.48,0:10:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Valge Island?! The Princess is there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.07,0:10:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.24,0:10:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Holy cow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.16,0:10:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,This thing is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.04,0:10:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.\NIt's the only Balloon Ship in Papnica.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.75,0:10:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, what a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.67,0:11:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,When you came from the sky,\NI thought you were the Princess, Miss Amy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.72,0:11:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no. The Princess is far more beautiful\Nthan I could ever hope to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.98,0:11:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh. I can't wait to meet her!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.02,0:11:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Gross. You're such a creep.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.40,0:11:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh come on! This is a princess\Nwe're talking about here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.61,0:11:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Who wouldn't be interested?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.57,0:11:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet she's gentle and cute,\Nunlike someone I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.70,0:11:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.12,0:11:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Leona's cute, but she's not really gentle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.83,0:11:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.58,0:11:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,She's brutally honest.\NShe could be worse than Maam.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.09,0:11:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If she's worse than Maam,\Nis she really okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.22,0:11:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.09,0:11:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,If she's worse than Maam,\Nshe must be an ogre.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.93,0:11:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.23,0:11:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Behave yourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.07,0:11:58.61,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}HYADARUKO{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}\NICE-TYPE SPELL
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.03,0:12:03.61,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,HELL'S CLAW
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.45,0:12:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,There's the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.71,0:12:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's Valge Island?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.30,0:12:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The sea is spinning!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.10,0:12:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the Valge Whirlpool.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.81,0:12:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of that,\Nmost people avoid Valge Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.52,0:12:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,To get there by boat requires taking a\Nlong route to avoid the whirlpool.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.48,0:12:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus Valge Tower\Nis the only thing on that island.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.95,0:12:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I never would have guessed\NHer Majesty was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.53,0:12:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all thanks to this Balloon Ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.41,0:12:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We used it as a message ship while we\Nplanned for a counterattack at the tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.75,0:12:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That must be the tower\Nin the middle of the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.92,0:13:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It used to be used as a lighthouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.59,0:13:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That's where Leona is!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.22,0:13:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At last... At long last I can see Leona!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.68,0:13:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.60,0:13:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! It's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.39,0:13:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.73,0:13:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.19,0:13:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.57,0:13:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?! What is going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.44,0:13:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir Apollo! Lady Marin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.69,0:13:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,They're fighting over rations!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.49,0:13:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Over rations?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.03,0:13:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough!\NYou're embarrassing yourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.79,0:13:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's his fault!\NHe tried to take more than his share!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.83,0:13:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been on guard for three days!\NI deserve to eat this much!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.46,0:13:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't eaten anything in a whole day!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.17,0:13:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.18,0:13:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.63,0:13:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hand that over!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.26,0:13:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.64,0:13:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.19,0:14:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.94,0:14:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Throwing it away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.86,0:14:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.99,0:14:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's the last of our valuable food!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.78,0:14:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Valuable or not,\Nif it sparks conflict, I don't want it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.50,0:14:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,All of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.04,0:14:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason we're in hiding\Nand preparing for a counterattack...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.29,0:14:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,is to thwart the Dark Army's evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.67,0:14:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,How can we fight amongst ourselves\Nover our own greed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.30,0:14:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's no different from the Dark Army!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.39,0:14:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If the alternative is to live as monsters,\Nthen let us starve to death as a humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.06,0:14:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so ashamed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.15,0:14:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You've barely eaten, too, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.78,0:14:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And here we are, the first to complain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.78,0:14:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.58,0:14:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We're sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.91,0:14:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you calmed down?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.37,0:15:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.58,0:15:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Then talk it over and share.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.42,0:15:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.51,0:15:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We just need to hold out a little longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.01,0:15:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I know the Hero will come to save us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.39,0:15:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean the young man\Nyou always speak of?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.40,0:15:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe his name is Dai?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.19,0:15:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.36,0:15:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a little short,\Nbut he's got the Hero spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.49,0:15:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I sent him a tutor,\Nso he should have gotten stronger by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.16,0:15:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not a very nice way\Nto speak of our savior.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.96,0:15:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But do think such a boy will really come?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.71,0:15:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us believe he will.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.01,0:15:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,At the very least, the Princess believes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.80,0:15:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,If the Princess believes,\Nthen so should we all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.55,0:15:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sorry, but that's\Na pipe dream right there.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.97,0:16:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Hero and company\Nare at the bottom of a pool of lava.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.14,0:16:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.40,0:16:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Such leadership and charisma\Nfor a little girl.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.94,0:16:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I may have scored\Na bigger fish than I thought.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.03,0:16:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.28,0:16:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You! Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.49,0:16:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Blizzblaze General Flazzard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.58,0:16:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry I ain't your Hero, little Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.54,0:16:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The Dark Army!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.50,0:16:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Curse you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.80,0:16:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,One was burned and one was frozen...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.85,0:16:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He can control both heat and cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.52,0:16:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Time to die now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.40,0:16:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Today the Papnica royal family dies out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.36,0:16:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.69,0:16:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't let you lay a finger\Non the Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.70,0:16:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Die, monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.62,0:17:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We can stand this flame!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.37,0:17:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Too hot for you?\NThen let me cool you down!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.43,0:17:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,With one blow?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.80,0:17:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The temperature difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.26,0:17:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The rapid temperature difference of\Nthe flames and ice weakened their armour!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.98,0:17:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.52,0:17:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like we got at least one guy\Nwith some brains.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.32,0:17:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Apollo of the Papnica Troika!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.11,0:17:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And I am Marin!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.95,0:17:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We shall protect the Princess\Nwith our lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.08,0:17:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh. Good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.37,0:17:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Marin, hit his flame side\Nwith a Hyado spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.04,0:17:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall hit the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.88,0:17:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.04,0:17:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Here goes! {\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Merazoma!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.96,0:17:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Hyadain!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.05,0:17:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoops!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.43,0:18:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodie, goodie.\NGiving me a feast as a welcome?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.98,0:18:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! He's absorbing the spell energy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.49,0:18:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Right back at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.66,0:18:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Fubaha!{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.50,0:18:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Fubaha, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.25,0:18:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, well. I guess that "Troika" title\Nain't just for show.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.00,0:18:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Now matter how strong your flames or ice,\Nyou cannot pierce this defensive shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.47,0:18:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.93,0:18:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Then out of respect for your performance,\Nlet me show you a neat trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.56,0:18:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,A trick?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.23,0:18:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Me...{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.57,0:18:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}ra...{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.99,0:18:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}zo...{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.53,0:18:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}oo...{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.16,0:19:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}ma!{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.04,0:19:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Five Finger Flares!{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.97,0:19:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! Something's wrong down there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.01,0:19:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Could the Princess be in danger?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.98,0:19:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He fired five Merazoma spells at once.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.23,0:19:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's an unbelievable monster!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.16,0:19:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Apollo, let me heal you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.21,0:19:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You bastard!\NHow could you do that to Marin?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.17,0:19:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make me laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.96,0:20:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a battlefield!\NIt doesn't matter who you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.68,0:20:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The strong live and the weak die!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.14,0:20:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't want to get hurt,\Nstay off of the battlefield!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.77,0:20:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ain't that right, Princess Leona?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.86,0:20:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You're prepared to die\Nin any horrible way, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.99,0:20:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry! Get us down there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.50,0:20:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you land on the roof?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.12,0:20:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, my lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.71,0:20:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Leona...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.25,0:20:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Hyado!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.72,0:20:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So much for Papnica.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.43,0:20:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,When the survivors hear of your death,\Nthey'll all lose hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.89,0:20:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure they'll never think of\Nopposing the Dark Army again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.19,0:20:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't assume humans are like you monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.15,0:21:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.86,0:21:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,There will always be someone\Nwho'll stand against you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.74,0:21:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So long as humanity has its pride!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.66,0:21:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's some courage there.\NRight when you're about to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.67,0:21:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye, little Princess.\NGo act tough on your way to the afterlife!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.05,0:21:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait... that knife...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.68,0:21:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.47,0:21:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.06,0:21:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You?! You're alive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.60,0:21:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Get away from Leona!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.73,0:21:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Save it for someone who cares!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.11,0:21:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If you even touch Leona, you'll regret it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.20,0:21:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.37,0:21:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You little brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.23,0:22:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kindness is the magic of kind people{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.23,0:22:25.99,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}yasashisa wa yasashii hito ga tsukaeru mahou{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.15,0:22:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then do I have no choice\NBut to just be a normal person?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.15,0:22:32.99,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}jaa boku wa tada no hito de iru shikanaino?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.16,0:22:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm not sure{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.16,0:22:36.21,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}doudarou{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.50,0:22:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if the place I call home may change{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.50,0:22:44.17,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kaeru basho wa ne kawatte yuku kedo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.34,0:22:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Listen to me, Mother{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.34,0:22:46.72,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}naa kaasan boku wa{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.88,0:22:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will never change those I protect{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.88,0:22:52.85,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mamoru hito wo kaetari shinai{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.31,0:22:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder what you'd say{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.31,0:22:57.52,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}anata wa nannte iukana{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.69,0:23:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At times I can be cowardly and small{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.69,0:23:01.73,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tokiyori yowaki de chippoke de{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.90,0:23:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What would you say to me\NAs I hesitate to even hesitate?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.90,0:23:08.20,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mayou koto ni mo mayou boku ni nannte iukana{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.36,0:23:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Unlike the today that I sought{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.36,0:23:14.03,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}sagashite ita kyou to chigatte{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.20,0:23:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sure you'd laugh at my disappointment{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.20,0:23:19.33,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ochikonnde shimau boku wo warau no darou{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.39,0:23:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dai battles Blizzblaze General Flazzard.{\i0}
